TransAlta Careers
Powering Possibilities
Great companies are built by great people, so what does TransAlta look for in people to join our team?
Our corporate culture is one that has been cultivated throughout our more than 100-year heritage of pioneering innovative ways to safely generate reliable, responsible and affordable electricity. It is the power of our values that connects us as a team, and we aim to acquire talent that aligns well with our core values.
Work ethic is one thing, but in addition, a TransAlta team member drives for results by taking accountability for his or her work. We take pride in our workplace where we are loyal to one another and respectful in our working relations. Integrity is the foundation of our business and through our employees’ leadership, TransAlta will lead the way to a clean power future.
Our people enjoy:

Competitive pay, benefits, vacation plans and personal days
Retirement plans
… and much more. To see how much, take a look at our Total Rewards.

Is TransAlta right for you?
Do you consider respect, loyalty, and integrity to be essential factors when it comes to the success of businesses? If yes, check out our current career opportunities.

 
 

