Leading us into the future
 
Our team of Corporate Officers and Senior Managers have diverse industry experience in both regulated and deregulated markets. Team members understand the advantage of generating electricity from a variety of fuel sources, and they know how to develop new projects, integrate acquisitions, operate in extreme and varied conditions, improve efficiencies, and to make the most of the power we create.
Shareholders are represented by a Board of Directors that has a comprehensive understanding of the electricity, resource, finance and regulatory sectors. Proven leaders in their own careers, they have also been recognized as a Board by the Globe and Mail every year since 2002 for overseeing one of the best-governed corporations in Canada.
Watch a video message from President and CEO Dawn Farrell.
 
 
 
 
  
 
 
 
 
 








