Customers
Securing your energy future.
In ever growing population, new clean technologies, a recovering economy and new ideas about how businesses want their energy needs met all point to the need for a sustainable energy future. It is time to make some of the decisions that previous generations also had to make to have reliable and affordable electricity.
TransAlta offers customers the opportunity to manage energy costs, secure energy supply, optimize energy assets and minimize your environmental footprint. As Canada’s largest publicly traded power generator and marketer of renewable energy, we continue to invest in clean and low carbon emission sources of electricity generation to maintain market advantage for decades to come.
Base your decisions on our advantage – the TransAlta advantage. We have been responsibly producing and securing reliable electricity for 100 years while becoming a leader in sustainable development. Make smart economic decisions that balance a shared and growing obligation to the environment. We can help.
Check out our Customer page if you’re an existing customer or if you’re looking to partner with TransAlta. We have retail and wholesale products for a number of businesses, including:

Commercial And Retailers
Municipal and Public Sector
Industrial, Manufacturing and Mining
Oil and Gas


 
 





